type="user">jms-00X4</fr:addr><fr:route>jms-00X4.xml</fr:route><fr:title
text="Querying a coslice of the transclusion preorder">Querying a coslice of the transclusion preorder</fr:title><fr:taxon>Example</fr:taxon></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p>We can also write a query to compute the set of trees <fr:em>underneath</fr:em> a given tree in the transclusion preorder (including the original tree) — in other words, the coslice.</fr:p><fr:pre><![CDATA[\def\query/transclusion-coslice[x]{
 \open\query
 \rel{\paths}{\outgoing}{\rel/transclusion}{\x}
}]]></fr:pre></fr:mainmatter></fr:tree></fr:mainmatter></fr:tree><fr:tree
